<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 12:41:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>万事达卡将以高达 18 亿美元的价格收购稳定币初创公司 BVNK</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/mastercard-to-buy-stablecoin-startup-bvnk-for-up-to-1-8-billion</link><description>万事达卡公司表示，将以高达 18 亿美元的价格收购稳定币基础设施初创公司 BVNK，四个月前，BVNK 与 Coinbase Global Inc. 就一项约 20 亿美元的交易进行的谈判破裂。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ittMqtxNQ0ro/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 12:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/mastercard-to-buy-stablecoin-startup-bvnk-for-up-to-1-8-billion</guid></item><item><title>人工智能的货币机器人已经到来，每个人都想处理他们的现金</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/the-race-to-bank-ai-agents-in-new-era-of-commerce-is-heating-up</link><description>多年来，稳定币行业一直在等待它的杀手级应用程序——通过为全球范围内的日常​​商业提供动力，该用例将证明数字美元不仅仅是加密货币投机者的工具。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVsyfxBqANMw/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/the-race-to-bank-ai-agents-in-new-era-of-commerce-is-heating-up</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争震撼市场时，比特币作为平静的绿洲令人惊讶</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/bitcoin-surprises-as-oasis-of-calm-while-iran-war-jolts-markets</link><description>自与伊朗的战争爆发以来，加密货币已成为资产类别中的赢家，但数字资产的弹性可能只是时间问题。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iq.WbBpsI2Kk/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 17 Mar 2026 06:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-17/bitcoin-surprises-as-oasis-of-calm-while-iran-war-jolts-markets</guid></item><item><title>随着投资者涌入 ETF，比特币触及六周高位</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-climbs-in-asia-as-other-markets-remain-tepid</link><description>由于投资者乐观地认为与中东冲突有关的市场动荡可能开始缓解，比特币升至近六周高点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ibHEfIi.8Ch8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 05:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-climbs-in-asia-as-other-markets-remain-tepid</guid></item><item><title>Saylor 的策略提高了最新比特币购买中优先股的销量</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/saylor-s-strategy-ramps-up-sales-of-preferred-in-latest-bitcoin-purchase</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 购买了价值近 16 亿美元的比特币，这是该公司自 1 月份以来最大的一次购买，该公司更加依赖于一种证券，该证券向投资者承诺，由同一加密货币支持的年度支付率为 11.5%。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ia_d3C2k3snA/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 14:13:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/saylor-s-strategy-ramps-up-sales-of-preferred-in-latest-bitcoin-purchase</guid></item><item><title>加密货币经纪商 BlockFills 在抛售后申请破产</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/crypto-trading-firm-blockfills-files-for-chapter-11-in-delaware</link><description>总部位于芝加哥的加密货币经纪和交易平台 BlockFills 在经历了数月的市场动荡，给整个行业的公司带来压力后，已申请破产保护。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i.C2p51ZhHtk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 07:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/crypto-trading-firm-blockfills-files-for-chapter-11-in-delaware</guid></item><item><title>伊朗“旧经济”资产抢尽风头，比特币陷入困境</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-btc-in-iran-limbo-as-old-economy-assets-steal-limelight</link><description>比特币今年大部分时间都在 60,000 美元至 75,000 美元之间徘徊，反复酝酿突破，但从未真正实现突破。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iu4OnECC9wX0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Mar 2026 04:39:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-16/bitcoin-btc-in-iran-limbo-as-old-economy-assets-steal-limelight</guid></item></channel></rss>